___INSTALLATION___
1) npm install --save @angular/material @angular/cdk @angular/animations
2) update your @NgModule to include necessary imports/declarations/entry components
3) add "@import '~@angular/material/prebuilt-themes/deeppurple-amber.css';" or an angular material theme of your choice to styles.css
4) add "@import 'app/NotifierService/notifier-service.css';" to styles.css
5) import the NotifierService to any components/services that will use it
6) use your shiny new NotifierService methods!

___NOTIFIER SERVICE DOCUMENTATION___
openDialog(): Opens a dialog
openActionSnackBar(message: string, action: string, color?: string): Opens a snack bar that can be dismissed by pressing the action button
openDurationSnackBar(message: string, duration: number, color?: string): Opens a snack bar that dismisses itself after a given duration
